  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "With regard to #6237 it might be useful for some deployment to configure the latency in which builder usage for a given public key is actually deactivated on BN.\r\nIn case users are using proposer config file refresh option (and in future with an additional VC rest API), they could dynamically set `builder.enabled` to `false`.\r\n\r\n`VALIDATOR_REGISTRATION_EXPIRATION_EPOCHS` is currently governing how quickly BN reacts to that by expiring he validator registration.\r\n\r\nMaking it configurable with a BN parameter users can have adjust it if they want to.",
